---
title: Tender Pork Fillet & Truffle Mayo with Cheesy Baby Potatoes & Thyme-Hazelnut Topping
description: Does it get more decadent than truffles? Well, tonight we’re serving a truffle mayo on the side to accompany the real hard-to- resist superstar, a roasted and seasoned pork tenderloin. Succulent and wrapped in earthy seasoning it’s sure to win the heart of anyone who takes a bite, especially when the pork is served with herby nuts and cheesy potatoes.
